name: I Didn't Miss
description:
"I Didn't Miss" is a game made for the Brackey's Game Jame 2022.

You are a small spaceship, enjoying the views of space when a fleet of nitroglycerin filled attack ships charge at you. You have only a gun to protect yourself, but the bullets are not real.  The enemies, however do not know that.

This is my first game jam game, so don't judge it too harshly :)

Controls (also in game): 

A and D to move

Space to 'shoot'

R to restart

M to go to menu
